Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.58,0:00:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.42,0:00:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.78,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查到那家伙的底细了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收获不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全防护比预计还要严密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为情报厅是由战前就存在的数个情报组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及旧防卫局合并而成的最新行政组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，合田所属的战略影响调查会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在国内外情报收集、分析以及自卫军的行动等方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.77,0:02:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是找到许多非法操作情报的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钸的这件案子也是其中之一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙的经历呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从防卫局被挖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口气爬到现在的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是当时的记录并不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直就是吊车尾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一个无法摸清底细的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田在防卫局时代的长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是在某次事故中受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他到现在还是保留了当时的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如现在那样令人印象深刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂时停止挖他的底细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去接受课长的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熬夜之后马上就参加午餐会议啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#08 素食的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急集合各位不为别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要告诉各位面对近来接连发生的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该如何应对的方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.62,0:03:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前我想狠狠揍那个混蛋一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内厅的行为很明显是对我们施压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受过两次气后我可不想保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也跟你们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.57,0:03:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴上虽这么说，可是你最近好像常常去总理那边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.61,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想在我们脖子上套缰绳的不就是首相本人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她虽然是为了将社会的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从前政权贿赂案件移开所推出来的花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，她只可能成为朋友不会变成敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.13,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想少校这边也独自进行过调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在内阁情报厅之内对陆自直升机失控事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.77,0:04:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及前几天的钸运送事件很明显有人意图操作情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.14,0:04:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前虽然不确定内厅对这些事件有什么样的企图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我认为数次对我们施压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.12,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是政府内部想隐瞒某些事情的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别的11人事件也是一样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以面对首相暗杀未遂这种重大恐怖活动时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会把立场最接近的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.43,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排除在调查活动之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使总理是纸老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果对抗政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还是等于反咬主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此还是要继续吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是在等这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我来说明作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里提出来的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.56,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是自称个别的11人的个别犯罪集团所犯的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.37,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JNN电视台捐款非法挪用事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民援助团体爆炸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐吓对难民无偿提供义体的NP0团体的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:23.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,NPO：Non-Profit Organization 非营利性服务机构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下义体医生溺死事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,网路银行总经理被火车辗死事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民政党议员刺杀事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人气电子脑饶舌歌手“传说”枪杀事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南阳报社恐吓事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺总理暗杀未遂事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这九个事件当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往认为只有首相暗杀事件才有目击到嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.31,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我发现另一个事件也有目击到可能是嫌疑犯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我第一次听到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察厅不是一直拒绝提供情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟笑面男事件的时候不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们也本着相当的觉悟进行调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上那本来就是不必要的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是来自警方而是事件当事人自己取得的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南阳的记者吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.74,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往南阳报社因为对难民政策采取批判的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,办公大楼三度遭到个别的11人开枪射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.85,0:06:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在所有事件发生的时候防盗摄影机上每次都有拍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他名叫川岛翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大约一个月前开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.13,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以台湾素食厨师的身分在南阳报社附近的餐厅工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.90,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还发现他有担任自卫官的经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个情报从哪里来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.87,0:07:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发出他的脸部骨骼资料后得到军方情报部的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.75,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到最后我们的亲戚关系还是军方比警方亲近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我们怎么处置这家伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先抓住这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查他的思想和背景关系中隐藏的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前虽然不能确定内厅和个别的11人有何关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要了解他们藉由什么媒介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让Stand Alone的恐怖份子团体出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以看穿他们的意图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.54,0:07:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特与托古萨、斋藤、帕兹去抓川岛翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.41,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川与波玛除了继续挖掘合田的内幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同时还要检索调查首相暗杀未遂的实行犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样总算变得比较像我们课了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是搞不太懂这两个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别的11人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是其它七个事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然“解放难民”这句口号相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是怎样都找不到一致性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.32,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了犯罪声明上印的标志以外也没有任何共通点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这跟笑面男事件性质相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，这些模仿者的原始版本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该就是死守中国大使馆的那群人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟是他们最早自称个别的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是除了他们之外反而没有人这么称呼自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连我们也是在调查那个标志的过程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到某位思想家的评论才知道该怎么念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在Stand Alone型的事件当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:09:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形成动机的媒介者不必然就是原版，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我还是觉得使用这个标志的那群人比较有原创性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好难吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么啊?这不是义体人用食品吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃不死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,材料是90%的面筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及用氨基酸为基础材料的少量微机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，状况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有收获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经四天以上没回公寓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去报社那边监视看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们来得太晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是难得的情报 失去新鲜度后也没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，该怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要照这样继续监视下去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然以抓到他本人为最优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了重视可能性之外别无他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他应该还继续在恐吓南阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且到昨天为止还有到店里上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样做不怎么主动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了弥补数量不足我送援军过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三台塔奇克马并不能提高监视的效率啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这么说嘛，托古萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能在维持个体差异的状况下进行同步化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还追加了代理机能喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.24,0:10:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说起来就像能做“幽体分离”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就可以身体留在现场 源源不断地去撷取情报了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们把这个叫作“情报的宴会”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闲聊到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高IR系统的检索能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,IR系统：InformationRetrieval–System 包含N系统[汽车牌号自动读取系统]在内的情报检索系统的总称\N也作为危险预防系统，是公安监视网的组成部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,积极逮捕川岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宴会!宴会!宴会!宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——开宴会罗!宴会!宴会!\N少校什么时候装了这种设备啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近我们的确人手不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来以为假装要换装PKF型号的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一定会露出马脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会已经不在国内了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怀疑是内厅操作过情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在地方网路上找到有趣的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田学生时代的毕业论文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.79,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在培养社会性的前提下电子脑应尊重个性还是协调性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从生产者的立场来谈英雄论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内容出乎意料很令人感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像标题也有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他指出现在的社会构造里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电子脑随着“个体”的消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于无意识当中表现出追求协调性的倾向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应用这个原理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.65,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他认为可以将有意识地控制无意识大众的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创造成为社会系统的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在解构笑面男事件的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过光看写的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这篇文章完成的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比笑面男事件还要更早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来那家伙又学了情报化学、情报伦理、应用情报论等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一度曾于民间企业就职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在在义体技术和微机械制造上众所皆知的超级跨国企业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波赛顿工业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是当时的大日本技研
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用超速公路前往博多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我挪不出太多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你几点会到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟约定的时间一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到上次那家店如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不便在太公开的场合跟你见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起来很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.87,0:13:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近都不能好好回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那是什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是鳗鱼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点小事我还是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是用面筋和香菇当材料所做出来的假鳗鱼料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台湾素食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是所谓的“素菜”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.09,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自古以来乃一部分僧侣自己研发出来的特殊料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,类似精进料理吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精进料理：起源于平安时代的日本素食\N包含了禅宗的精进精神之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，跟日本精进料理不同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是不直接调理食材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.67,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是对豆类和香菇加工重现出肉或鱼的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你吃剩的三明治是同样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么台湾的和尚会想出这么麻烦的料理法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一开始就不知道肉的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就没有这种必要了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话是这么说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论是谁在进佛门之前都是可以随便吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.57,0:14:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管修行有多深还是无法消除当时的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，你还真是清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.18,0:14:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道老大也开始怀念起真正的味道了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是义体人脑部对食欲还是会有需求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.72,0:14:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会制造出当成娱乐使用的义体人食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.99,0:14:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了想起过去的记忆“味道”扮演再生装置的角色吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川岛那家伙是在哪里学到这种料理的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半是驻留台湾的时候学的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们几个好好监视喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然今晚的主题是难民问题和恐怖主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想先把这段时间的事情经过再整理一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.89,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去政策目标的政府之怠慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,促使个别主义者抬头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.86,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了在维新中找出答案的激进因子登上舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以这么解释吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是因为现在的政权太软弱才出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的政权上台之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国防出身的议员就在考虑签定新美日安保条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.84,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说现在动手可以从美国手中抢到主导权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.55,0:15:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别主义其实早跟这股潮流同时存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让个别主义者激进起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如说是浪费税金的三百万难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说我们国家已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多该处理那些家伙的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.53,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此，一开始就不要接收不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说出这句话就无法继续讨论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.47,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来的难民处理法强迫国民增加多少税金呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那些税金以难民处理当藉口都消失在黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——有谁在吗? ——这种只会引发犯罪的处置法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我把现在33频道播的政论节目的录影光碟拿过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——我知道了 ——执政党不知为何还不废除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——当然还要继续录影喔 ——那也无可奈何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果很快就去刺激难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们更是不会善罢甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗称的自爆恐怖攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是对自己的未来不抱任何希望之时的最终手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此有必要促使他们自发性的走向自立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他们名为解放的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算给难民自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们也不可能自己解决自己的问题不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.01,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去比对那台车的车牌号码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然已经针对数个恐怖活动讨论过整体案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们提出具体的问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——是那时候的 ——土桥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个警察厅一心想隐瞒的恐怖活动是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件本身我想大家也都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国大使馆占领事件以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您应该知道发生了八件左右的恐怖攻击事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指电子脑音乐家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有对难民主张和睦政策的议员被刺杀的事情吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这些事件当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个警察厅完全未对媒体公布的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要装模作样了，快点说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看过这个标志吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上是登记在连锁店名下的普通车辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送来当作犯罪声明的信件上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通通都印有这个标志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——这家伙为什么知道这个? ——从来没听过这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——怎么样？ ——我也没听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——监视都交给塔奇克马啦? ——情报来自哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——不...不是 ——那是企业机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——拿去 ——那就没有说服力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——不是吃东西的时候了 ——那要是知道这个标志的念法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——怎么啦?这可是真的喔 ——你们也多少会吃惊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.39,0:18:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——这家伙是我以前见过的记者之— ——这个标志读作个别的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——他竟然知道事件的机密情报 ——源自半世纪前某本评论集的篇名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.23,0:18:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用这个名称发动事件的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在解放难民的动机之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.73,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现没有横向联系的个别集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——这家伙在说什么啊 ——以自卫军直升机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在难民街上空盘旋为契机 个别主义者开始现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们这些行动者的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.61,0:18:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—— 竟然有这种感染案例啊 ——是真心想解放难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——因为不能过度降低警察的品格 ——抱歉打断各位讨论，我们进广告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他是很好的点火角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.79,0:19:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外，南阳事件和首相暗杀事件的感染者呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.83,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于南阳的感染者已经对公安1课操纵完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想很快就能清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于尝试暗杀首相的感染者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜想可能是因为PKF去半岛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名叫久世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是透过感染因子反推回去所得到的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想应该没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于合田那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算问防卫局时代的同僚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也几乎没有人记得他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.93,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只记得他很没有存在感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.57,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我找到了录用时的精神分析测验记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然内向，却有很强的自我意识和自我炫耀欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.58,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反过来说也有利用他人来表现自己的倾向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟现在的他感觉上多少有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?不吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道跟以前一样没变喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟以前一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.40,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你上次问的那个叫作川岛的自卫官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公安1课也向我们询问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是一个叫王崇廉的杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷了川岛的脸躲在中华街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以来跟我们要脸的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事为什么不早说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为你已经跟他们联络过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.39,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1课会调查跟南阳不同的案子实在很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点通知巴特他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经在通知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到王崇廉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是台湾出身的国际恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面虽然下达了暗杀命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是没接到他变脸的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我们被陷害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是1课被陷害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是哪一种这个时间点实在很微妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了以防万一控制住刚刚那辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标在店后面出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这个国家给难民住太奢侈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也还没富裕到可以收容难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是王崇廉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Roger
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把枪放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.80,0:21:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巷子太窄没办法帮他挡子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是1课的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔细看看这家伙的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.09,0:22:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没有连脸都义体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说他不是王崇廉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.76,0:22:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.33,0:22:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1课得到了确实的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.87,0:22:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是素子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也被设计了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.61,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.76,0:23:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.60,0:23:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字——然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.27,0:23:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.38,0:23:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我——时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.51,0:23:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相，所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.02,0:23:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的——它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.02,0:24:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.29,0:24:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字——然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.00,0:24:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.04,0:24:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我——时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.24,0:24:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相，所有我需要
